- They need you on the rig.

24
00:01:04.815 --> 00:01:06.584
Hey. you know there's a
ton of trees out there. right?

25
00:01:06.608 --> 00:01:08.002
Yeah. they'll give us a lot of shade.

26
00:01:08.026 --> 00:01:10.839
Hey. About these trees...
Yeah. we need the shade.

27
00:01:10.863 --> 00:01:12.298
- But do we?
- Sorry. we're running late.

28
00:01:12.322 --> 00:01:15.093
- Okay. Have a great day.
- Bye. I... bye. girls. Bye.

29
00:01:15.117 --> 00:01:16.511
- Come on. Let's go.
- Bye.

30
00:01:16.535 --> 00:01:18.078
- Hey. Coop.
- Hey. Bye.

31
00:01:21.123 --> 00:01:22.100
You walk or drive?

32
00:01:22.124 --> 00:01:23.643
I walked. You told me to walk.

33
00:01:23.667 --> 00:01:25.586
Right. We're taking my car.

34
00:01:26.837 --> 00:01:27.838
Come on.

35
00:01:28.881 --> 00:01:29.881
Okay.

