See. I can't come down
on her about her spending

44
00:01:53.947 --> 00:01:55.466
if I'm driving a fucking rolls.

45
00:01:55.490 --> 00:01:57.117
Come on. You love it.

46
00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.078
It is a hell of a car.

47
00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:03.540
It is so choice.

48
00:02:04.208 --> 00:02:05.292
I'm driving.

49
00:02:07.419 --> 00:02:08.419
Sure.

50
00:02:35.572 --> 00:02:37.491
What the fuck?

51
00:04:07.289 --> 00:04:08.683
So where are we going anyway?

52
00:04:08.707 --> 00:04:10.435
We are going to see a lawyer.

53
00:04:10.459 --> 00:04:12.937
Barney. I can't sue Bailey Russell.
They'll squash me like a bug.

54
00:04:12.961 --> 00:04:15.088
I'm sorry. I should have been more clear.

55
00:04:15.631 --> 00:04:17.882
We are going to see Rick massiello.

56
00:04:19.885 --> 00:04:22.405
You got an appointment with massey?
How'd you get an appointment with massey?

57
00:04:22.429 --> 00:04:23.490
It doesn't matter.

58
00:04:23.514 --> 00:04:26.808
Point is. as soon as Bailey
hears his name. they'll settle.

59
00:04:27.518 --> 00:04:28.870
The last thing Jack wants

60
00:04:28.894 --> 00:04:31.539
is massey putting on a big
show and rattling his investors.

61
00:04:31.563 --> 00:04:32.999
He will be expensive.

62
00:04:33.023 --> 00:04:35.126
Well. he'll do it on contingency.

63
00:04:35.150 --> 00:04:37.837
- He told you that?
- Not as such. but you'll convince him.

64
00:04:37.861 --> 00:04:40.006
- He's gonna take half.
- Probably.

65
00:04:40.030 --> 00:04:42.592
But that other half is a lot
more than you have now.

66
00:04:42.616 --> 00:04:44.802
You have bills to pay. my
friend. Starting with mine.

67
00:04:44.826 --> 00:04:46.161
<i>Nick brandes.</i>

68
00:04:48.622 --> 00:04:49.682
Nick! Hey.

69
00:04:49.706 --> 00:04:50.808
<i>What's good. Barney?</i>

70
00:04:50.832 --> 00:04:53.353
Just checking in on
that "refi" for the gym.

71
00:04:53.377 --> 00:04:55.772
Dobbs is saying we can
fund the next two locations

72
00:04:55.796 --> 00:04:57.690
<i>without liquidating any
of my market positions.</i>

73
00:04:57.714 --> 00:04:59.150
Yeah. Hey. sorry. Nick.

74
00:04:59.174 --> 00:05:00.652
I'm in the car with Coop.

75
00:05:00.676 --> 00:05:02.070
<i>- I'm on speaker?</i>
- Yeah.

76
00:05:02.094 --> 00:05:03.738
<i>Hey. What's up. Coop?</i>

77
00:05:03.762 --> 00:05:06.491
You guys know the women have
that self-defense thing tonight?

78
00:05:06.515 --> 00:05:08.701
- Is that tonight?
- <i>That's what I'm told.</i>

79
00:05:08.725 --> 00:05:10.912
<i>We're all bachelors tonight. fellas.</i>

80
00:05:10.936 --> 00:05:14.123
So I'm gonna get some meat and
booze and have everyone over to hang.

81
00:05:14.147 --> 00:05:15.708
<i>- You guys in?</i>
- Sounds good.

82
00:05:15.732 --> 00:05:17.335
<i>Yes. sir. What about you. Coop?</i>

83
00:05:17.359 --> 00:05:18.360
Hard pass. Nick.

84
00:05:19.111 --> 00:05:23.633
Yeah. Well. the invitation
stands if you change your mind.

85
00:05:23.657 --> 00:05:25.617
Yeah. I won't. But thanks.

86
00:05:28.996 --> 00:05:30.849
Well. I'm gonna hang up
before this gets awkward.

87
00:05:30.873 --> 00:05:32.684
- See you tonight. Nick.
- <i>All right. Barney.</i>

88
00:05:32.708 --> 00:05:34.418
<i>Hit me back about the "refi."</i>

89
00:05:38.130 --> 00:05:40.108
- What?
- What happened to team Coop?

90
00:05:40.132 --> 00:05:41.943
You told me there are no teams.

91
00:05:41.967 --> 00:05:44.487
But if there were. obviously I'm on yours.

92
00:05:44.511 --> 00:05:47.157
- Fuck Nick.
- But you'll go over to his house.

93
00:05:47.181 --> 00:05:48.700
The man throws a good party.

94
00:05:48.724 --> 00:05:50.285
You should go.

95
00:05:50.309 --> 00:05:51.602
You shouldn't.

96
00:05:52.728 --> 00:05:54.789
Well. as of a few days ago
Nick is my biggest client.

97
00:05:54.813 --> 00:05:56.499
so my hands are tied.

98
00:05:56.523 --> 00:05:57.774
Wow.

99
00:05:58.358 --> 00:05:59.919
Shame if something
happened to this car.

100
00:05:59.943 --> 00:06:01.862
Do not even joke about that.

101
00:06:06.617 --> 00:06:07.760
You can't win.

102
00:06:07.784 --> 00:06:09.429
I just gotta say that up front.

103
00:06:09.453 --> 00:06:12.581
You're a smart guy. Coop. You know
you can't go the distance with these guys.

104
00:06:14.374 --> 00:06:15.393
Well. thanks for your time.

105
00:06:15.417 --> 00:06:17.520
Good news is you don't have to win.

106
00:06:17.544 --> 00:06:19.147
You just gotta get
past summary judgment

107
00:06:19.171 --> 00:06:21.649
at which point Bailey
will start making offers.

108
00:06:21.673 --> 00:06:23.568
Then it becomes a negotiation.

109
00:06:23.592 --> 00:06:25.528
And I'm a great fucking negotiator.

110
00:06:25.552 --> 00:06:27.596
Will you do it on contingency?

111
00:06:28.430 --> 00:06:29.491
No.

112
00:06:29.515 --> 00:06:31.493
I gotta charge you full
freight on this one. pal.

113
