That's a prototype.

759
00:42:22.918 --> 00:42:24.711
I am so...

760
00:42:27.130 --> 00:42:29.091
<i>If you're in the market for metaphors...</i>

761
00:42:30.384 --> 00:42:33.947
<i>Look no further than a man
vomiting into a $30.000 toilet</i>

762
00:42:33.971 --> 00:42:35.514
<i>that isn't connected to any plumbing.</i>

763
00:42:38.976 --> 00:42:41.663
<i>Though. once you get
into a certain frame of mind.</i>

764
00:42:41.687 --> 00:42:44.439
<i>everything in this town
is a fucking metaphor.</i>

765
00:42:45.440 --> 00:42:49.778
