figure out what. if anything. is real.</i>

766
00:43:17.222 --> 00:43:18.473
Have a good day.

767
00:43:22.644 --> 00:43:23.812
Hey. hunter.

768
00:43:50.422 --> 00:43:51.691
Hey. you.

769
00:43:51.715 --> 00:43:52.817
Hey.

770
00:43:52.841 --> 00:43:53.985
I stopped by your house.

771
