823
00:46:21.907 --> 00:46:24.117
I don't know. but we're
gonna make it a priority.

824
00:46:25.035 --> 00:46:27.704
- Really?
- No. Not really.

825
00:46:44.930 --> 00:46:47.242
<i>The paper clip. now
wired to the battery pack.</i>

826
00:46:47.266 --> 00:46:48.934
