831
00:47:01.446 --> 00:47:03.907
<i>Now. gonna introduce our voltage.</i>

832
00:47:06.076 --> 00:47:11.290
<i>Voilà. And if that doesn't
work. there's always brute force.</i>

833
00:47:18.797 --> 00:47:20.483
<i>My shrink would've had a field day</i>

834
00:47:20.507 --> 00:47:24.553
<i>unpacking the fact that I was stealing
from the guy who slept with my wife.</i>

835
